Package com.terturl.MMO.MMOEntity.ResourcePack

Class ResourcePackGenerator

java.lang.Object
com.terturl.MMO.MMOEntity.ResourcePack.ResourcePackGenerator
public class ResourcePackGenerator extends Object
Will create the information needed to create a resource pack that will be able to display the newly created MMOMob to all players on the server, if they do not have this resource pack, the MMOMob will be a collection of saddles on their screen
Since:
0.58.0
Author:
Sean Rahman
